New pImgDB. Also newest version of my XMP class.


List of stuff thsi pile of shit can do:
- Help->Documentation to view test images
- Left/right to change image
- Play button for slideshow
- Doubleclick play to set delay
- Click image to close it


Buttons above sidebar:
- Press X to hide/show
- Press box to undock


Blingage (desktop image display):
- Select images in thumbnail mode
- View->Blingage->Add selection
- View->Blingage->Show blingage
--- Drag it to move it
--- Next/prev buttons... yeah
--- Play button start/stop slideshow
--- X button closes it


Also, Debug->Display shows how the image
loader is working as you change images
with left/right buttons.
